why can't i find stuff in my place? i lose every thing and then i look every where and the stuff is just gone. i live in a one bedroom apartment so where the hell is my stuff hiding. the main things are my very cool sandels that i bought during the winter and have never even worn them yet. also my sisters old drivers licence that i use as i.d. to get in to the bars. i am soo angery right now. 
also i took my antideppresants to close together and now i feel super sick and i'm sweating way to much on my hands. 
i think i'm ready for something else, something in a different demention, something magical and happy.
i've served my time as a human, now i want to go somewhere where people/creatures are always nice,, there is no people who kill, steal, cheat or abuse. there are no victoms struggling to survive in a cold evil world. every thing and every one is always alive and joyful.
